<p><a name="Importance_and_impact" id="Importance_and_impact"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Bloody_Sunday_(1972)&amp;action=edit&amp;section=15" title="Edit section: Importance and impact">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Importance and impact</span></h3>
<ul>
